{"tid":2386451,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【有片】教埋你點整 仲有藉口唔用TG?","createTime":"2021-01-29T14:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T16:06:39.000Z","uid":142519,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab65931abba1d9da33d20984f665e462baf0a486","tid":2386451,"uid":142519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">去睇片先</span></span><br />\n原po: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100331115059955/posts/230701945356204/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100331115059955%2Fposts%2F230701945356204%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=cff50c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100331115059955/posts/230701945356204/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7L111nA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7L111nA.png&h=51c0e516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCB5JBi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCB5JBi.jpg&h=42b0ddc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【手動分享|簡易教學】<br />\n想棄用Whatsapp 但又唔捨得啲對話？<br />\n<br />\n即睇以下教學同分享俾同路人啦！👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n【如何將Whatsapp對話連多媒體轉移至Telegram ?】（暫時只限IOS用戶）<br />\n<br />\n近日，Telegram 推出了 7.4 的最新版本。<br />\n這次更新主要加入匯入WhatsApp、Line，韓國 KakaoTalk 通訊軟件的聊天記錄新功能，以進一步改善用戶由其他社交軟件轉至Telegram 的體驗。<br />\n<br />\n更新至Telegram 7.4版後，用戶將可選擇保留WhatsApp 與聯絡人及群組對話，揀選 Export Chat匯出聊天記錄，並選擇以Telegram開啟該檔，再選擇或新增聯絡人或群組。<br />\n<br />\n詳情請參考《幽光》為大家準備的教學影片。<br />\n<br />\n影片：幽班記<br />\n編：杏仁露<br />\n<br />\n#whatsapptotelegram #Whatsapp #Telegram #網絡安全<br />\n_____<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/luminanthk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fluminanthk%2F&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=cc141496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.co